  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Sound Theme Freedesktop</title>

    <para>
      <application>Sound Theme Freedesktop</application> is a collection of sounds that can be applied to specific events.
      eg when a file is opened, login/logout etc.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

